Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.23,0:00:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, let's do our best.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.19,0:00:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you can draw without resting.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:08.02,0:00:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.57,0:00:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make our dreams come true.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.24,0:00:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.16,0:00:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I cant tell him to stop drawing.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.88,0:01:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.22,0:01:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.39,0:02:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.72,0:02:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.60,0:02:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.60,0:02:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro, Takagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.56,0:02:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be frank.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.19,0:02:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The editorial department is going ahead with their plans to put you on hiatus with chapter 20 in issue 33.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.69,0:02:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:19.16,0:02:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't go on hiatus.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.95,0:02:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.92,0:02:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.25,0:02:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'll tell them when I get back to the office.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.80,0:02:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll also tell them I think you can draw in the hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.55,0:02:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.35,0:02:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.18,0:02:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's already this late?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.14,0:02:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Saiko, don't push yourself too hard. Get some sleep, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.65,0:02:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can't go to school, so I should be able to get some decent sleep.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.24,0:03:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, I think I can make a clean copy of the rest of chapter 20's storyboard by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:02.99,0:03:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't need to.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.24,0:03:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can understand the story well enough from Takagi's version.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.66,0:03:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll work it out with Takagi and make sure you can get started on the manuscript by Saturday, as usual.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's head out, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.09,0:03:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's still a bit of time left, isn't there?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We might as well stay...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.18,0:03:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.14,0:03:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, whats with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.89,0:03:24.14,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.18,0:03:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, that Shuujin.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.27,0:03:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He did something he didn't need to.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.44,0:03:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come every day I can.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.02,0:03:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.53,0:03:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm worried... and I can't email you here.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.61,0:03:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can use my cell phone if I step outside the hospital...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.91,0:03:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be able to turn it on if I go out into the courtyard.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone does it.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.66,0:03:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll be fine. You don't need to worry so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.46,0:03:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It may contradict what I said before,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but being able to see you makes me happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.72,0:04:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's limit it to until you're released from the hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.97,0:04:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I keep coming?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.18,0:04:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it bother you?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I might also be contradicting myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.98,0:04:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm with you, I get embarrassed and my heart starts pounding...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.94,0:04:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but it also calms me down.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I want us to be together forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.78,0:04:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But only until I'm discharged.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.79,0:04:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.87,0:04:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Get well soon!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I got sick.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.63,0:04:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like I'll have some good memories of being here with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mashiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.76,0:04:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it bother you that we decided to stay apart until our dreams come true?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.22,0:04:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.06,0:04:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's hard sometimes,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.06,0:04:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and after I get discharged it'll be hard to go back to being apart from you,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.40,0:05:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's exactly why I can push myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.69,0:05:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see you soon.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.40,0:05:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.45,0:05:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Until our dreams come true.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.21,0:05:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm saying I think he can still draw! I don't want to force them to go on hiatus!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Miura?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.80,0:05:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we can at least put the bit that the assistants finish up into issue 32.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.34,0:05:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.93,0:05:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I will still put out the hiatus \Nannouncement from issue 33 onwards.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.64,0:05:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.81,0:05:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me you received permission to let him draw from his doctor?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll accompany you to the hospital tomorrow.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I can't count on you to get the job done.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.68,0:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.53,0:05:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The patient is saying that if he is not allowed to draw, his stress will increase, and it will be bad for his health.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.87,0:05:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It is true that patients should be allowed to do as they like in moderation.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.33,0:05:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Only in moderation.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.54,0:05:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't push myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.67,0:06:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.34,0:06:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry to barge in, ma'am.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the editor-in-chief—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.64,0:06:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.22,0:06:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking care of my son.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.89,0:06:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You've met before?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.64,0:06:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something I should mention here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.15,0:06:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We are to blame for the current situation, and I offer my deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.98,0:06:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you aren't... Moritaka!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop drawing manga in your hospital room!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.16,0:06:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, the doctor said it was fine in moderation...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.58,0:06:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't be able to do it "in moderation"!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.12,0:06:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it isn't good to be too persistent.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.50,0:06:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll rest a bit.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.13,0:06:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name was Sasaki, correct?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.88,0:06:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.59,0:06:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband said that he's not a child anymore, and to let him continue on the path he chose.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But I just can't...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.93,0:06:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rest assured, we will not let any harm come to him.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.52,0:07:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yoshida...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.65,0:07:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I should go visit Ashirogi in the hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.36,0:07:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you hear about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We tried to keep it quiet.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.94,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't reveal my source.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.82,0:07:11.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd dry it up, of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.57,0:07:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Niizuma won't pick up my calls anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.53,0:07:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, I've barged into Ashirogi's before, and they took care of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.29,0:07:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only proper that I go visit them.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.83,0:07:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A mangaka isn't a real member of society.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So cruel!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a member of society anymore?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already a caged bird.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.80,0:07:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm Mr. Yoshida's pet dog.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.63,0:07:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not allowed to act like a human anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.55,0:07:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wasn't here, you'd look up his hospital and go anyways, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just go on Monday and get it over with, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.18,0:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange, I'll be going with you, and we're coming back right away.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.69,0:07:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.77,0:07:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard Mashiro is in the hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.23,0:07:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard from Aida.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.11,0:07:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I also heard that they're on hiatus starting from issue 33.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.95,0:07:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Going on hiatus after finally getting popular...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What bad luck.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Niizuma already went to see him.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.91,0:07:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going on Monday, wanna come?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.58,0:08:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pushing it every week. I don't have that kind of time!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.46,0:08:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't be so cold.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.79,0:08:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If I invite Miss Aoki, she'll be sure to come.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.21,0:08:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Aoki will?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.09,0:08:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really pushing my deadline.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.09,0:08:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you stop tempting me like that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.34,0:08:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about Mashiro, but I just can't...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.72,0:08:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'll just tell him you're concerned for him, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What? She did?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.85,0:08:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and she even propped up Saiko with her own hands.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.69,0:08:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought they weren't even gonna hold hands until they got married.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.36,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's she thinking?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.20,0:08:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd think she would stop him.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.61,0:08:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this showed me once again how much she really does like him.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I don't get it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.29,0:08:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate love is accepting everything your partner wishes for, and helping to achieve it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.50,0:08:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And perhaps cooperating with them as well. {like, working together with them, maybe}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.80,0:08:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I would be too worried about his health and stop him.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki's got a strong will.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.93,0:09:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And she really loves Saiko.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.18,0:09:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it does take some strength to stay apart until their dreams come true.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They met, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.52,0:09:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Can they go back to staying apart now?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.73,0:09:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If they kiss in the hospital or something, I bet they won't be able to!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiss~
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going with that?{sarcastic, not in a good or interested way}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.45,0:09:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever, you don't understand a woman's heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, the storyboard's done.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.12,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give it to Saiko even if there's fixes to be made.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.54,0:09:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Back on track!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.71,0:09:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,H-He's still drawing even though he's been hospitalized!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.88,0:09:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And his girlfriend is cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.92,0:09:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of tough to work in here, and it's a bit cramped, but I can't allow a break in our serialization.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.84,0:09:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Look well.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.47,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he the model mangaka?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.02,0:09:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you drawn to this kind of lifestyle, Miss Girlfriend?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.90,0:09:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.02,0:09:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Yoshida, when we return, I will definitely draw.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.36,0:09:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I was mistaken...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.90,0:09:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you were.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.65,0:09:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You should feel ashamed of yourself, Hiramaru.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.70,0:10:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, if it isn't the escape artist Hiramaru.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.16,0:10:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.83,0:10:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.87,0:10:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the author of {\i1}Kiyoshi Knight{\i0}, Fukuda.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.38,0:10:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You met him earlier at Niizuma's house, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.13,0:10:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.05,0:10:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for taking care of me then, Fukuda.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.51,0:10:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kiyoshi {\i0}'s the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.05,0:10:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give me your contact information and the address of your office, if you would...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.55,0:10:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:21.93,0:10:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not even really reading Jack, are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.31,0:10:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously though, seeing you work while hospitalized has given me a better opinion of you, Mashiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.65,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to you all.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.44,0:10:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just talking about him being a model mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.11,0:10:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I laughed at the "Wanted: Hiramaru" fax from Yoshida.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:40.53,0:10:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are {\i1}you{\i0} laughing?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.62,0:10:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm glad that you're lively enough to draw the manuscript.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.29,0:10:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty loud in here for a hospital room.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.62,0:10:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Editor!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.45,0:10:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize, but I must ask everyone but Mashiro and Takagi to leave the room.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.55,0:11:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we have to leave?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.34,0:11:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because this has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.31,0:11:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it does, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.47,0:11:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ashirogi Muto are my comrades.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Comrades?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're soft.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.31,0:11:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, it's written as "comrade" but read as "rival". {lit. the furigana abov the word will read "rival"}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.82,0:11:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, you may stay.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.82,0:11:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Azuki, you stay too.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.00,0:11:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, this is a hospital. No matter what I say, don't make a fuss.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.67,0:11:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it something we'd make a fuss over?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.55,0:11:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, we had a meeting regarding what to do with {\i1}Shady Detective Trap{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:43.18,0:11:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shady Detective Trap{\i0} will be put on hiatus until next April, when the authors graduate from high school.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.61,0:12:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Next April?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.86,0:12:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that? I don't get it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.20,0:12:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to make a fuss.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kind of jealous.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.99,0:12:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,W—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.41,0:12:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.33,0:12:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why April instead of when he's discharged?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.04,0:12:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.50,0:12:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura, you told us it was fine to start this storyboard on Saturday!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.09,0:12:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the reason?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please explain this to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.18,0:12:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hear it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.22,0:12:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because Kawaguchi Tarou died.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.73,0:12:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The death of my uncle and our \Nserialization have nothing in common.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.49,0:12:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.15,0:12:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Died?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.95,0:12:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There was someone I knew who worked too hard on manga and died.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.91,0:12:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The person he told me about, that was his...?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.12,0:12:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawaguchi Tarou was Mashiro's uncle on his father's side.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.13,0:13:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,His death is firmly linked to his occupation as a mangaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.09,0:13:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be a stretch to say that he was a victim of manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.68,0:13:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother is worried and wants you to stop drawing manga entirely.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she does.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.73,0:13:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No one wants to lose their family, the ones they love.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.23,0:13:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't rest.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.40,0:13:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll draw.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.78,0:13:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kawaguchi Tarou never broke a serialization deadline even once.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.12,0:13:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when he had a fever above 40°...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.43,0:13:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when he strained his back and couldn't sit up,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.00,0:13:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,he drew his manuscript while lying down.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He never went on hiatus even once.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.08,0:13:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,600)}He said he was proud of that, at least.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.17,0:13:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That is an old-fashioned way of thinking, but it's respectable that you don't want a hiatus.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.05,0:13:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But when the editorial department decides you need rest, then you must rest.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.18,0:13:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need rest!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.02,0:13:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me be clear.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.39,0:13:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Continuing to draw would trouble all of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.59,0:14:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Get better first.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.32,0:14:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after he gets better, he's still on hiatus until April.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.15,0:14:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you contradicting yourself by telling him to get better, then not picking the serialization back up?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.74,0:14:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The genius high schooler Niizuma Eiji.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.33,0:14:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We were impressed with his performance in serialization, so the editorial board approved serializing authors in high school. {possibly take 'after serialization' out of the first part, dunno}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.50,0:14:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But a weekly serialization isn't that easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was our mistake.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.97,0:14:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We regret it, and will refrain from\N approving such serializations in the future.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Refrain?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.35,0:14:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But serializations that have already started should be another matter!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.43,0:14:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're irresponsible for starting this policy now!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.96,0:14:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll quit school!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There shouldn't be a problem then!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.48,0:14:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you do that, I won't lift the hiatus until April!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.32,0:14:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What Ashirogi's saying makes more sense!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Put yourself in their parents' positions!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.28,0:14:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dropping out of high school to draw manga.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Will your parents be happy with that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.21,0:14:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't live for my parents!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.83,0:15:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Our lives are our own!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Until April?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.50,0:15:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A special Sunday meeting was held yesterday, and that's what was decided upon.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.63,0:15:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Why until April?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that strange?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.43,0:15:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was interested as well, so I asked the vice-editor, but all he said was "It'll be a problem if he dies on us."
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.23,0:15:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Aida, do you know who Kawaguchi Tarou was?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.98,0:15:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He was the one-hit-wonder who made Super Hero Legend.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.15,0:15:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't want to end his career with just that, so he continued writing storyboards and eventually died from overwork. {overworking? not too sure}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.07,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just a rumor, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.70,0:15:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No, apparently, it's the truth.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.33,0:15:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,His real name was Mashiro Nobuhiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.46,0:15:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He was none other than Mashiro's uncle.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.38,0:15:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.71,0:15:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they had no choice, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.96,0:15:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That's messed up.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.59,0:15:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuujirou!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.88,0:15:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not allowed to draw until April because he's Kawaguchi Tarou's relative?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.01,0:15:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unbelievable!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.89,0:15:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.47,0:15:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We're ignoring Mashiro's... no, Ashirogi Muto's feelings!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.85,0:16:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kawaguchi Tarou wasn't my uncle...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.64,0:16:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't be doing this.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.44,0:16:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.11,0:16:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.98,0:16:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awful.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.16,0:16:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that lame excuse?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.95,0:16:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't listen to this!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.67,0:16:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiramaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.58,0:16:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.38,0:16:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where? Where else would I go but back to my room to draw manga?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.34,0:16:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like he said.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.97,0:16:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura, this is your fault, too, you yes-man.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.81,0:16:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.89,0:16:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not Miura's fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.14,0:16:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,On the contrary, he resisted until the very end.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.46,0:16:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}my{\i0} decision.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.90,0:16:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't accept this "hiatus until April" bull.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.44,0:16:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,See you all later, Ashirogi.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.12,0:16:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it again.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.70,0:17:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you draw, I won't publish it until April.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.37,0:17:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you regain your health and graduate high school, I promise to restart the serialization then.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.84,0:17:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura, I'm headed back.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stay.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.05,0:17:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:18.18,0:17:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.35,0:17:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this April thing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.93,0:17:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Takagi, Mashiro, I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.81,0:17:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as you saw— I have no authority.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.69,0:17:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.31,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.28,0:17:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who needs to apologize.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.82,0:17:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To you, Shuujin... and Azuki too.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.74,0:17:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't gotten sick...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:43.02,0:17:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.04,0:17:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the chief editor's decision!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.42,0:17:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and it's also due to my powerlessness.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.26,0:17:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need to apologize to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.88,0:18:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The words I said to you the day we graduated middle school... will hold true forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.97,0:18:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Take your time to get better.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.14,0:18:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about graduation day?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.94,0:18:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, even if I ask, you probably won't tell me.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I'd always be waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.82,0:18:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Azuki...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.03,0:18:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So she is worried about his health.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll always be waiting", huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.16,0:18:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.54,0:18:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive the chief editor for putting Ashirogi in that situation.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.09,0:18:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.71,0:18:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's irrational.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.67,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't draw for Jack until he withdraws his decision.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.92,0:18:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.47,0:18:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I'm the only one doing that, it won't make a big impact.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.89,0:18:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.97,0:18:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If they're making {\i1}Trap{\i0} take a break, then I'll take a break too!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.39,0:18:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But won't Ashirogi feel guilty about that?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.65,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we're going to keep this quiet from them,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.32,0:18:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,and only tell them after the editor withdraws his decision.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.65,0:18:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.86,0:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll convince Nakai and Aoki.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! The entire Fukuda Team will boycott!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.66,0:19:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not all.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.54,0:19:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Boycott!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.00,0:19:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's wonderful, it's fun, and tomorrow just got a bit brighter.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.29,0:19:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,April is just too long.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.01,0:19:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got no choice.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking about a person's life here!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.26,0:19:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, please tell us about yesterday's meeting in more detail!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.43,0:19:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuujirou, cut it out.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.43,0:19:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you stopping me?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.72,0:19:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't go along with it this time!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.69,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Right, I feel bad for Ashirogi!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.69,0:19:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Chief Editor is back!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.91,0:19:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boycott?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.87,0:19:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't draw {\i1}Kiyoshi{\i0}, {\i1}Crow{\i0}, or {\i1}Otters 11{\i0} until he withdraws his decision.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.37,0:19:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No objection.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.33,0:19:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And if he doesn't give in, I'll draw for another magazine until Ashirogi can draw again. {maybe a different word aside from draw here}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.00,0:19:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going that far?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.63,0:19:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have a contract, so you can't do that...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.30,0:20:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll return the down payment and do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.38,0:20:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If it comes down to it, I'll pay the termination fees for Ashirogi and everyone else so we can migrate to another magazine!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.14,0:20:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to keep drawing manga, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But, well...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.89,0:20:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakai, you're not manly enough at times like these.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.06,0:20:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that the Chief Editor is going too far.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.61,0:20:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We should fight against it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.53,0:20:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Miss Aoki, this is the first time we've agreed on something.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:21.90,0:20:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For a boycott, the more people we have, the better.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.49,0:20:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on fire today!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I also like you.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.95,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Hiramaru!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.20,0:20:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to pull in this confusion? {This is far too explict for what he says though}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.71,0:20:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.54,0:20:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I'm weak against beautiful women.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.63,0:20:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.21,0:20:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about them, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.63,0:20:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.89,0:20:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, welcome back.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.99,0:21:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.86,0:21:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too quiet in here.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.71,0:21:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard about Ashirogi.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.53,0:21:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.53,0:21:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awful.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.58,0:21:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just keep quiet about this.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.54,0:21:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's protest it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.08,0:21:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the Chief Editor is just outside.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.88,0:21:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it down.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.46,0:21:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And even if you protest, there's no way he'd change his mind once it's made up.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.43,0:21:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Fukuda?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.09,0:21:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Boycott?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.89,0:21:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.72,0:21:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,"If arrangements are not made for {\i1}Trap{\i0}'s early return, we will also go on hiatus."
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.98,0:21:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"We..."?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.36,0:21:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kiyoshi Knight{\i0}, {\i1}Crow{\i0}, {\i1}Otters 11{\i0}...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.82,0:21:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Otters{\i0} as well?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.69,0:21:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, {\i1}Hideout Door{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.03,0:21:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hi-door{\i0} too?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.82,0:21:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They each took the phone and announced it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.95,0:21:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's five series counting {\i1}Trap{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.04,0:21:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a huge problem if they all go on hiatus!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.91,0:21:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.54,0:21:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they've gone out of their way to tell us about the boycott, I'm going to let the Chief Editor know.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.63,0:22:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't, idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.00,0:22:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the editors' job to make the authors draw!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.34,0:22:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just accept it quietly!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.05,0:22:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuujirou, everyone was on the same phone, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.72,0:22:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.55,0:22:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means they're all in the same place right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.60,0:22:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go. Try asking them where they are.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.93,0:22:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.19,0:22:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in charge of Fukuda and Niizuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.60,0:22:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a problem regarding {\i1}Trap{\i0}, so I'll come too.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.02,0:22:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming too.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.90,0:22:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, when we leave the department, let's go in ones and twos so we don't raise suspicion.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.41,0:22:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. At the nearest family restaurant. There are five of us here.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.79,0:22:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All of our editors, plus Hattori, are coming in secret without the Chief Editor knowing.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.67,0:22:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They're taking us on!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.58,0:22:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a battle between authors and editors!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.59,0:22:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! EXCITING!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:15.51,0:24:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We're boycotting until the decision about Ashirogi's hiatus is reversed!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.35,0:24:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like an unprecedented situation will occur.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:20.31,0:24:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unprecedented that you and I agree on something!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.94,0:24:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Bakuman:
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.98,0:24:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Recall and Call.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.98,0:24:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive a guy who crushes dreams!
