Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:44.35,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,The fight doesn't end until I fulfill my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:50.60,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wonder how far I've come now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.60,0:00:55.90,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,In ten years, I'll be living the dream
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.90,0:01:02.41,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the scenario I wrote for myself, so I'll have no regrets
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:09.04,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,But life isn't that easy, and it's full of obstacles
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:15.38,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,900)}Still, I swear to myself that I won't ever back down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:24.09,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a dream that I absolutely want to achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.09,0:01:30.35,Lyrics-Eng,,0,0,0,,So I fuel my passion until I succeed
